      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよこの日が来たな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally‚ the day has come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 6.4929251608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、本当にいろいろありましたけど\nなんとか、本番に間に合いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ there were really a lot of things going on‚\nbut somehow‚ I made it in time for the performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ミクと握手会に出たり、作詞も初めてで大変だったけど\n何もかもが新鮮で、楽しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku and I joined the greeting event and wrote lyrics. It was tough‚\nbut everything was fresh and enjoyable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "その全てが、今日のステージのためだ\n期待してるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everything you've been through was for today's stage.\nI'm expecting great things from you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 25.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、ミクと私達TRINITYAiLEで\n最高のステージにしてみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ together with Miku and our TRINITYAiLE‚\nwe'll make it the best stage ever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 31.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "本当に、ありがとうございました\nこの日のために、沢山助けてくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much\nfor helping me so much for this day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 37.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺は大したことはしてないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven't done anything significant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、そうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 42.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ミクとはいろんなことを話しましたけど\n{user}さんにとても感謝してましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had many conversations with Miku‚\nand she was really grateful to you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "少しアドバイスを送っただけだよ\nミクとはどんなことを話したんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just gave a little advice.\nWhat did you talk about with Miku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 53.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "気になりますか？　でも、内緒です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you curious? But it's a secret.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 59.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "一体何を話したんだ？\n……おっと、そろそろ出番だな。準備は出来てるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C'mon‚ what did you talk about?\n…Oops‚ it's about time. Are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1866.6666666999986,
          "startTime": 58.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 63.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです\nミクと私達とで、最高のステージを届けてきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nTogether with Miku and all of us‚ we'll deliver the best stage ever!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも\nしっかり観ていて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san too‚\nplease watch closely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0866073687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 74.2
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 74.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、マジカルミライにようこそ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ welcome to Magical Mirai!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ミクと私達、四人での初めてのステージですけど\n楽しんでいただけていますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's our first stage together with Miku‚ the four of us.\nAre you enjoying it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "ミクの気持ち――みんなへの感謝の気持ちを\n曲に込めて、歌います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll sing with gratitude from Miku's heart to everyone‚\nincorporating those feelings into the songs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "それでは聴いて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please listen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.666666599997,
          "startTime": 93.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "（凄い声援……ミクが好きっていう強い気持ちが）\n（観客席から伝わってくる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Amazing cheers… The strong feeling that people love Miku)\n(It's transmitted from the audience)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "（バーチャル・シンガー……誰かのために）\n（歌い続けてきたミクだから、こんなにも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(As a virtual singer….Because Miku)\n(has been singing for someone til now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "（自分のためじゃなくて）\n（誰かのために歌い続けてきたからこその、強さ――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Not for herself)\n(The strength that comes from that…is very strong.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6333.333333300005,
          "startTime": 119.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 119.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 119.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、とてもいいステージだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job‚ it was a really great stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n……今日のライブ、とても勉強になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much.\n…Today's live performance was very enlightening for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 129.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。ミクは――バーチャル・シンガーは\n今まで出会ったアイドルとは違うものな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Miku‚ being a virtual singer‚\nis different from the idols you've met before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（彼女との共演は、天動さんにとって）\n（大きな刺激になったようだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Her collaboration with Miku seems to have been)\n(a significant stimulus for Tendo-san)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 142.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "はい、本当に、凄く違ったんです。私とミクは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it was really different. Miku and I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "頭では分っていたんですけど\nミクと同じステージに立って、改めて実感しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understood it intellectually‚\nbut standing on the same stage as Miku made me realize it again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 156.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "私達は、トップアイドルを目指して\nライブバトルで戦って、ランキングを競い合っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We are aiming to be top idols‚\nbattling in live performances and competing in rankings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "でも、VENUSプログラムの外側にだって\nあんなに凄い子がいて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even outside the VENUS program‚\nthere are amazing individuals…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 170.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……大丈夫か？　少し元気がないようだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you okay? You seem a little down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "あ……いえ、少し考え込んでしまって……\nあの、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… No‚ I was just lost in thought…\nUm‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 183.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "私は、誰のためでもなく、自分のために\nアイドルの道を選びました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I chose to be an idol not for anyone else‚\nbut for myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui024.m4a",
      "text": "でも……いつしか、父に認めてもらえるくらい\n凄いアイドルになることに、囚われていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… Somehow‚ I became obsessed with becoming an amazing idol\nto earn my father's approval.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 199.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "今はもう違うだろ？\n誰かに認めてもらうためでも、自分のためでもない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not the case anymore‚ right?\nIt's not about seeking approval from someone or for yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さんと奥山さんと三人で\nトップに立つために頑張ってるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You‚ Suzumura-san‚ and Okuyama-san are working hard\nto stand at the top together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui025.m4a",
      "text": "そうです。でも……ミクと同じステージに立って\n疑問が浮かんだんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. But… standing on the same stage as Miku‚\nI had a question in my mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 217.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui026.m4a",
      "text": "私の歌は、もしかしたらミクの歌ほど\nファンの心に届いてないんじゃないかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe my songs don't reach the fans' hearts\nas much as Miku's songs do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそんなことを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why would you think that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 227.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui027.m4a",
      "text": "私は父に認めてもらうため、仲間のために歌ってきた\nそれと比べて、ミクはずっと純粋です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been singing for my father's approval‚ for the sake of my comrades.\nIn comparison‚ Miku is always pure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui028.m4a",
      "text": "ただファンのことを、強く、純粋に想って歌う\nだから私の歌よりも、心に響くんじゃないかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She simply sings with a strong‚ pure love for her fans.\nSo I wonder if my songs resonate in their hearts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 246.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui029.m4a",
      "text": "教えて下さい、{user}さん\n私、ちゃんとファンに向き合えて、いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please tell me‚ {user}-san.\nAm I truly facing my fans properly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "天動さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 256.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui030.m4a",
      "text": "私、何言ってるんだろ。ごめんなさい。忘れて下さい\n今日はお疲れ様でした。失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What am I saying? I'm sorry. Please forget it.\nThank you for today. Goodbye.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 264.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（……ミクとの共演で受けた刺激が）\n（いい方向に働けばいいんだけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…If the stimulus from collaborating with Miku)\n(works in a positive direction‚ it would be great.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}